title: Surfing dog
description:
Dice the Australian Shepherd hits the surf at Wreck Beach, Sleaford Bay, South Australia. Shot with Canon XF300 and Contour GPS.

Music by Waylon Thornton "Look for Danger" under Creative Commons licence.
